(28, 'h5', '', '<h5>For someone to contact you, complete the form below...Or head to our booking website by clicking on the button here Everything can be booked and bought on this site</h5>\r\n', 'h5For someone to contact you, complete the form below...Or head to our booking website by clicking on the button here Everything can be booked and bought on this site', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 18:21:37', '2022-01-20 17:48:32', NULL),
(29, 'p', '', '<p>Indoor leagues and games to train and play year round in a competitive setting</p>\r\n', 'pIndoor leagues and games to train and play year round in a competitive setting', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 18:21:57', '2022-01-20 17:48:35', NULL),
(30, 'p', '', '<p>All of our instructors are highly qualified and have played sports at high school, collegiate, and professional levels. We have a passion for all sports and want every athlete that joins our BB Sports Family to develop that same passion.</p>\r\n', 'pAll of our instructors are highly qualified and have played sports at high school, collegiate, and professional levels. We have a passion for all sports and want every athlete that joins our BB Sports Family to develop\r\n                    that same passion.', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 18:22:23', '2022-01-20 17:48:38', NULL),
(31, 'h5', '', '<h5>Recruiting Services</h5>\r\n', 'h5Recruiting Services', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 18:42:40', '2022-01-20 17:48:40', NULL),
(32, 'p', '', '<p>Our top of the line program!!! This is our pride and joy program that is built from programs like the New York Yankees, Toronto Blue Jays, Los Angeles Dodgers, Washington Nationals, Colorado Rockies, Miami Marlins, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use technology such as hittrax, rapsodo, diamond kinetics, and more. Included is a full Athletic Performance Evaluation testing mobility, strength, and sports specific skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Train like the Professionals!!!</p>\r\n', 'pOur top of the line program!!!', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 18:47:27', '2022-01-20 17:48:42', NULL),
(33, 'p', '', '<p>Train in a 1 on 1 or 2 on 1 setting. We offer hitting, pitching, fielding, catching, speed and agility, and strength training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All of our instructors and trainers have a background in baseball and softball and played at the collegiate and/or pro level. We use technology such as hittrax, rapsodo, diamond kinetics, and more.</p>\r\n', 'pTrain in a 1 on 1 or 2 on 1 setting', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 18:49:42', '2022-01-20 17:48:44', NULL),
(34, 'p', '', '<p>Can&#39;t make it into the facility? No problem!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have online lessons at the palm of your hand. Our head instructor has been doing video analysis for youth, high school, college, and pro athletes for the last 5 years with over 5000 hours of video analysis work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>He has been working with brand new and veteran athletes at BB Sports for 3 years developing some of the best drill progressions. These drill progressions are designed to fix any flaws in the quickest and most efficient ways</p>\r\n', 'pCan\'t make it into the facility', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 18:53:26', '2022-01-20 17:48:47', NULL),
(35, 'p', '', '<p>Recruiting Services</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Get access to the knowledge and resources needed to get recruited!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We build recruiting videos, give you email templates, add you to our Player Portal, and talk you through the process of sending videos and information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t miss out on getting recruited by not being proactive or not knowing where to start. Let us help!!</p>\r\n', 'pGet access to the knowledge and resources', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 18:56:41', '2022-01-20 17:48:49', NULL),
(37, 'h5', '', '<h5><u>Our Top of the Line Programs</u></h5>\r\n', 'h5Our Top of the Line Program', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 19:25:04', '2022-01-20 17:48:52', NULL),
(38, 'p', '', '<p>This is our top of the line training program for serious athletes that are looking to play college and pro ball!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This is our highly advanced training program that focuses on the skills, biomechanics, and mobility/strength needed to preform at the highest level!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Must be willing to commit to a weekly commitment at a determined time that best fits instructors and athletes/family.</p>\r\n', 'pThis is our top of the line training program for serious athletes', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 20:32:07', '2022-01-20 17:48:58', NULL),
(39, 'h2', '', '<h2>sssssssss</h2>\r\n', 'h2HittingIncrease…Exit Velocity', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 20:44:43', '2022-01-20 17:49:00', NULL),
(40, 'h2', '', '<h2>Hitting</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase...</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exit Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Distance</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(Bat Path, Hand Path, Spine Stability, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Consistency</li>\r\n	<li>Pitch Recognition</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'h2HittingIncreaseExit Velocity', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 20:50:25', '2022-01-20 17:49:02', NULL),
(41, 'h2', '', '<h2>Fielding</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase...</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Footwork</li>\r\n	<li>Glove Work</li>\r\n	<li>Glove WorkAwareness</li>\r\n	<li>Bad Hop Reactions</li>\r\n	<li>Pre Pitch Planning</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'h2FieldingIncreaseFootwork', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 20:53:01', '2022-01-20 17:49:06', NULL),
(42, 'h2', '', '<h2>Velocity and Pitching</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase...</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Throwing Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Spin</li>\r\n	<li>Leg Drive</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(arm action, hand position, shoulder alignment, hip rotation, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Control</li>\r\n	<li>Offspeed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'h2VelocityandPitchingIncreaseThrowing Velocity', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 21:32:46', '2022-01-20 17:49:09', NULL),
(43, 'h2', '', '<h2>Strength, Speed, and Power</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase&hellip;</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobility</li>\r\n	<li>Strength</li>\r\n	<li>Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Agility</li>\r\n	<li>Explosion</li>\r\n	<li>Power in Multiple Planes</li>\r\n	<li>Body Awareness</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'h2StrengthSpeedandPowerIncreaseMobility', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 21:34:24', '2022-01-20 17:49:11', NULL),
(44, 'h2', '', '<h2>Youth Athleticism</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase&hellip;</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hand Eye Coordination</li>\r\n	<li>Motor Skills</li>\r\n	<li>Strength</li>\r\n	<li>Agility</li>\r\n	<li>Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Acceleration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'h2YouthAthleticismIncreaseHandEye', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 21:36:52', '2022-01-20 17:49:14', NULL),
(45, 'p', '', '<p>We are looking for committed athletes that are wanting to elevate their game to that next Peak Top and continue their passion for the game.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We have you fill out a form that gives us the best days and times to fit your schedule and our schedule! We have groups running almost everyday!!</p>\r\n', 'pWe are looking for committed athletes that are wanting', 1, 0, '2022-01-14 21:39:52', '2022-01-20 17:49:16', NULL),
(46, 'h5', '', '<h5>Private Lessons and Training</h5>\r\n', 'Private Lessons and Training', 1, 0, '2022-01-17 18:40:06', '2022-01-20 17:49:18', NULL),
(47, 'p', '', '<p>Forget the cookie cutter programs!!! At BB Sports we do everything custom to each athlete!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full Athletic Performance Evaluations are done for each one of our athletes!! We test mobility, strength, and sports specific skills to design the perfect progression that is custom to each athlete!!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We use the most advanced technology available to track numerous metrics. Hittrax, Rapsodo, 4D motion, Pocket Radar, Strength Sensors, etc. are all used to get the most accurate numbers possible to track and design programs</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hitting, Pitching, Velocity, Fielding, Catching, Strength, and Speed/Agility are all offered and run by instructors with college or pro experience!</p>\r\n', 'pForget the cookie cutter programs', 1, 0, '2022-01-17 18:41:24', '2022-01-20 17:49:20', NULL),
(48, 'h5', '', '<h2>Hitting</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exit Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(Bat Path, Hand Path, Spine Stability, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Consistency</li>\r\n	<li>Pitch Recognition</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>', 'h5Private Lessons and Training', 1, 0, '2022-01-17 18:45:35', '2022-01-20 17:50:01', NULL),
(49, 'h5', '', '<h2>Hitting</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Exit Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Bat Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(Bat Path, Hand Path, Spine Stability, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Consistency</li>\r\n	<li>Pitch Recognition</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>', 'plh5HittingIncrease', 1, 0, '2022-01-17 18:47:15', '2022-01-20 17:50:05', NULL),
(50, 'h5', '', '<h2>Fielding</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Fielding Percentage</li>\r\n	<li>Rhythm</li>\r\n	<li>Footwork</li>\r\n	<li>Glove work</li>\r\n	<li>Bad Hop Reactions</li>\r\n	<li>Bad Hop Reactions</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>', 'plh5FieldingIncrease', 1, 0, '2022-01-17 18:48:13', '2022-01-20 17:50:07', NULL),
(51, 'h5', '', '<h2>Strength/Mobility Speed/Explosion</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mobility</li>\r\n	<li>Strength</li>\r\n	<li>Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Agility</li>\r\n	<li>Explosion</li>\r\n	<li>Power in Multiple Planes</li>\r\n	<li>Body Awareness</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'plh5StrengthMobilitySpeedExplosionIncrease', 1, 0, '2022-01-17 18:49:09', '2022-01-20 17:50:09', NULL),
(52, 'h5', '', '<h2>Pitching/Velocity</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Throwing Velocity</li>\r\n	<li>Spin</li>\r\n	<li>Leg Drive</li>\r\n	<li>Biomechanics(arm action, hand position, shoulder alignment, hip rotation, etc.)</li>\r\n	<li>Control</li>\r\n	<li>Offspeed</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>', 'plh5PitchingVelocityIncrease', 1, 0, '2022-01-17 18:51:22', '2022-01-20 17:50:11', NULL),
(53, 'h5', '', '<h2>Catching</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Increase</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Blocking</li>\r\n	<li>Framing</li>\r\n	<li>Footwork</li>\r\n	<li>Foot Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Pop Times</li>\r\n	<li>Transfer Times</li>\r\n	<li>And More</li>\r\n</ul>', 'plh5CatchingIncrease', 1, 0, '2022-01-17 18:54:08', '2022-01-20 17:50:13', NULL),
(54, 'h5', '', '<h5>ELEVATE YOUR GAME</h5>\r\n', 'h5ELEVATE YOUR GAME', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 12:58:56', '2022-01-20 17:50:16', NULL),
(55, 'h2', '', '<h2>BB SPORTS ONLINE TRAINING</h2>\r\n', 'h2BB SPORTS ONLINE TRAINING', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 13:38:24', '2022-01-20 17:50:18', NULL),
(56, 'p', '', '<p>Our head instructor Shea Bell has done over 5000 hours of coaching and video analysis. He works with 10+ pro athletes, 20+ college athletes, and numerous high school and college athletes. Including players such as Chad Bell(3B, Yankees), JD Hammer(P, Phillies), Aaron Ochsenbein(P, Dodgers), Shane Matheny(IF, Giants), Ben Newton(C, ECU), and so many more</p>\r\n', 'pOur head instructor Shea Bell has done', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 13:39:45', '2022-01-20 17:50:19', NULL),
(57, 'h2', '', '<h2><u>WHAT SHOULD YOU EXPECT?</u></h2>\r\n', 'h2WHAT SHOULD YOU EXPECT?', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 14:52:51', '2022-01-20 17:50:23', NULL),
(58, 'h2', '', '<h3>1) Skills and Mobility Analysis</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Every client starts their first lesson with sending us 1 thing for breakdown and analysis</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hitting or Pitching Video</p>\r\n\r\n<p> <i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> Side view is the best for optimal analysis</p>\r\n', 'h31) Skills and Mobility Analysis', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 14:55:28', '2022-01-20 17:50:24', NULL),
(59, 'h2', '', '<h3>2) Easy Video Upload with APEX by Upper Hand</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Upload your videos all within APEX just by creating an account or having us create it for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You submit your video and within 48 hours you have a breakdown, analysis, and lesson plan</p>\r\n', 'h3WHAT SHOULD YOU EXPECT?', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 15:04:36', '2022-01-20 17:50:26', NULL),
(60, 'h3', '', '<h3>2) Easy Video Upload with APEX by Upper Hand</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Upload your videos all within APEX just by creating an account or having us create it for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You submit your video and within 48 hours you have a breakdown, analysis, and lesson plan</p>\r\n', 'h32) Easy Video Upload with APEX by Upper Hand', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 15:12:16', '2022-01-20 17:50:29', NULL),
(61, 'h3', '', '<h3>3)Top of the Line Evaluations</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our evaluations are always extremely in depth. I take the time to look at multiple angles(if provided) to find the most alarming issues.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>Hitting or Pitching Video<br />\r\nSide view is the best for optimal analysis</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>We then send a full in depth voiceover to show you what we see, what we mean by our terminology, and an in depth drill progression.</p>\r\n', 'h33)Top of the Line Evaluations', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 15:15:19', '2022-01-20 17:50:31', NULL),
(62, 'h3', '', '<h3>4) Lesson Plans</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our lessons are custom to each clients...we take the same process every time to find out why we are struggling and how to get better</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>Send in your video</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>We analyze your swing or throwing motion</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>Voiceover analysis explaining what we see</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>We send list of drills with videos examples and how to fix</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>Message us if you have questions on the drills we sent</p>\r\n', 'h34) Lesson Plans', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 15:20:22', '2022-01-20 17:50:33', NULL),
(63, 'h3', '', '<h3>5) Multiple Ways to Pay</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our 3 packages allow you to train at your pace. Find out what your doing wrong or stay consistent with</p>\r\n\r\n<p>multiple lessons...as low as $21 per lesson</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> 1 Lesson=$30</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> 4 Lessons=$100</p>\r\n\r\n<p><i class=\"fa fa-futbol-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> 8 Lessons=$175</p>\r\n', 'h35) Multiple Ways to Pay', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 15:24:05', '2022-01-20 17:50:42', NULL),
(64, 'p', '', '<p>Our youth teams the Colorado Yetis(Baseball) and Colorado Power(Softball) are some of the top programs in Northern Colorado.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We give the kids the basic fundamentals and athleticism to play any sport as far as they would like</p>\r\n', 'pOur youth teams the Colorado Yetis', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 15:34:29', '2022-01-20 17:50:45', NULL),
(65, 'p', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Develop individual skills that will help each player have success at every level</li>\r\n	<li>To learn game knowledge and situations taught at the professional level</li>\r\n	<li>To create athleticism and hand eye coordination that will help with all sports</li>\r\n	<li>To develop a passion for this great game and experience life lessons and experiences with your friends and BB Sports family</li>\r\n	<li>And overall to develop young men that will have success in life whether it is on the field or in life</li>\r\n</ul>', 'pDevelop individual skills that will help each player have success at every level', 1, 0, '2022-01-18 15:38:17', '2022-01-20 17:50:47', NULL),
